		<div><h3><b>1.</b> The video is sent in real time to the Splitter.</h3></div><br />
		<div><h3><b>2.</b> The Splitter divides the stream in several chunks and every chunk is sent to one different peer.</h3></div><br />
		<div><h3><b>3.</b> Each peer sends its chunks to each other in order to ensure that everyone has the whole stream.</h3></div><br />
		<div><h3><b>4.</b> Peers send the stream to the player.</h3></div>
 	</section>
