	<section>

		<h1>Pollution Attacks</h1><br />
		<h2>Pollution attacks consist of a peer or a set of peers modifying the content of the stream. Can be done in different ways.</h2><br />

	</section>
	<section>

		<h1>Pollution Attacks</h1><br />
		<h2><strong>Persistent attack</strong>: an attacker poisons every chunk received from the splitter and sends them to the entire team.</h2><br />
			<div>
				<img src="images/persistent-attack.svg" alt="Persistent Attack" height="500" style="margin:5px"/> <br />
</div>

	</section>

	<section>

		<h1>Pollution Attacks</h1><br />
		<h2><strong>On-Off attack</strong>: the attacker only poisons some chunks but not others.</h2><br />
		<div>
			<img src="images/on-off-attack.svg" alt="On-Off Attack" height="500" style="margin:5px"/> <br />

</div>		

	</section>

	<section>

		<h1>Pollution Attacks</h1><br />
		<h2><strong>Selective attack</strong>: poisoning chunks intended for only one peer or a small subset of peers.</h2><br />

			<div>
			<img src="images/selective-attack.svg" alt="Selective Attack" height="500" style="margin:5px"/> <br />

</div>	
	</section>

	<section>

		<h1>Pollution Attacks</h1><br />
		<h2><strong>Collaborative attack</strong>: several attackers may collaborate to produce Selective and On-off attacks on a large set of peers.</h2><br />

			<div>
			<img src="images/collaborative-attack.svg" alt="Collaborative Attack" height="500" style="margin:5px"/> <br />

</div>	

	</section>

	<section>

		<h1>Pollution Attacks</h1><br />
		<h2><strong>Hand-wash attack</strong>: leaving the team and returning to continue the attack with another alias.</h2><br />

			<div>
			<img src="images/hand-wash-attack.svg" alt="Hand-wash Attack" height="500" style="margin:5px"/> <br />

</div>	
	</section>

	<section>

		<h1>Pollution Attacks</h1><br />
		<h2><strong>Bad-mouth attack</strong>: blaming other regular peers of sending poisoned chunks or not sending chunks.</h2><br />

			<div>
			<img src="images/bad-mouth-attack.svg" alt="Bad-mouth Attack" height="500" style="margin:5px"/> <br />

</div>	

	</section>

