	<section>

		<h1>Proposals</h1><br />
		<h2>We present two different strategies aiming to mitigate the impact of pollution and related attacks by combining trust management, hashing/signatures and trusted peers.</h2><br />
		<br />		

		<div style="float:left; width:50%;" class="fragment">
			<h3>1. Strategy based on Trusted Peers. <br /> (STrPe)</h3> <br />
			<img src="images/tp.png" alt="Trusted Peers" height="200" /><br />
		</div>
		<div style="float:left; width:50%;"  class="fragment">
			<h3>2. Strategy based on Trusted Peers and Digital Signatures. <br /> (STrPe-DS)</h3> <br />
			<img src="images/tpds.png" alt="Trusted Peers and Digital Signatures" height="200" /><br />
		</div>

	</section>

	<section>
