	<section>

		<h1>How to make a decision about expelling peers from the team?</h1><br /><br />
		<div style="float:left; width:50%;" class="fragment">
			<img src="images/attack1.svg" alt="Attack 1" width="700" style="margin:5px"/> 				<br />
			<h2><center>Selective Attack</li></h2>
			<br />
		</div>
		<div style="float:left; width:50%;" class="fragment">
			<img src="images/attack2.svg" alt="Attack 2" width="700" style="margin:5px"/> 
			<br />
			<h2><center>Bad-mouth Attack</li></h2>
			<br />		
		</div>
		<br />		
		<h3 class="fragment" style="text-align: justify;">If three peers are complaining about one peer, it is difficult for the splitter to know whether there are three attackers trying to expel one well-intended peer or if it is actually one attacker poisoning three well-intended peers.</h3>

	</section>

